","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5916,"content":"入职的时候说的是13薪，一年调一次薪。第13薪 按照年终奖的形式发放，然后年终奖发了1K，满一年也不调薪，无语死了","createdAt":"2023-11-07T11:28:49"},{"id":"01963ddf-ad60-729f-bd10-8a0dfb83fa0f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7423,"content":"加班多，五险一金最低，福利少，喜欢绩效考核，项目少，勉强维持运转，不建议去","createdAt":"2024-05-08T17:31:55"},{"id":"01963ddf-ad11-7231-a209-308a281f9afb","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2271,"content":"没毛病老铁","createdAt":"2024-06-03T14:53:04"},{"id":"01963ddf-ada4-7145-b778-f308bb180479","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21427,"content":"不要来这个公司  用绩效来变相给员工降薪","createdAt":"2024-07-19T15:40:14"},{"id":"01963ddf-adea-716f-a872-46ff773cc589","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21427,"content":"以提升能力为借口 强制性单休。","createdAt":"2024-07-19T15:43:42"},{"id":"01963ddf-ae49-7152-89fa-0ab139a234fc","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3500,"content":"汇智智能科技公司？","createdAt":"2024-07-19T16:15:56"},{"id":"01963ddf-ae8e-73df-b095-51c5126b0a57","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21429,"content":"还真有那么多人来评论啊","createdAt":"2024-07-21T16:24:04"},{"id":"01963ddf-af19-7179-8954-502192702c7d","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21427,"content":"给十分制，满足九分及以上才发100%工资不满足则发90%、80%、60%； 在这基础上还以公司盈不盈利为标准 盈利了发100%工资 不盈利发90%工资","createdAt":"2024-09-09T08:57:26"},{"id":"01963ddf-af66-72e6-b232-f236ec63ee8f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21427,"content":"脸都不要了撒","createdAt":"2024-09-09T08:57:42"},{"id":"01963ddf-af5d-72de-a768-d7399949d71d","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":764,"content":"之前一纸通知直接给干成单休了，现在又是接着给降薪，恶心到家了","createdAt":"2024-09-09T09:45:20"},{"id":"01963ddf-af61-7241-a0e2-7b31a2afe6d9","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1978,"content":"《月度绩效考评表》做为《绩效考核管理制度》的一部分与绩效制度共同使用，请知悉","createdAt":"2024-09-09T10:33:40"},{"id":"01963ddf-afac-700d-ade1-9b2e2f7433c3","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21827,"content":"降薪，还要PUA你，是因为自己的原因导致降薪","createdAt":"2024-09-09T10:57:28"},{"id":"01963ddf-aff3-707a-b75c-e9a191b76f00","parentId":null,"rootId"